title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell.
OB: When exporting data from a table inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: Data export from a table inside a grid cell should not cause an exception to be thrown.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Insert a grid.
2. Insert a table into one grid cell.
3. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
4. Attempt to export the data from the tables.
